---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="footer">
  <div class="inner">
    <p class="line">
      Based on Charles Kay Ogden's <em>Basic English</em> (1930) · 850 words
    </p>
    <p class="line muted">
      字表來源：<a href="https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/Appendix:Basic_English_word_list" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Wiktionary</a>（CC BY-SA 4.0）·
      原始字母對照：<a href="https://archive.org/details/ogdens-basic-english-words-list-alphabetic" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Internet Archive</a>
    </p>
    <p class="line muted small">
      Crafted with care · {year} ·
      <a href="/about">關於</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .footer {
    margin-top: 96px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    padding: 48px 32px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .inner {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .line {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .line em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--op);
  }
  .muted {
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
  }
  .small {
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  .footer a {
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-color: var(--line);
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }
  .footer a:hover {
    color: var(--ink);
    text-decoration-color: var(--ink-faint);
  }
</style>
